# Creamy Apple Vinaigrette
### Serves: About 12

### Ingredients:

- ½ large apple, chopped (with peel on)
- ¼ cup white balsamic vinegar
- ½ cup vegetable or canola oil
- 2 tablespoons diced shallot
- 1 tablespoon Dijon mustard
- 1 tablespoon honey
- 1 tablespoon fresh lemon juice
- Salt and pepper to taste

### Procedure:
1. Place all ingredients in a blender and process until smooth. Cover and
refrigerate extra dressing, shaking to blend again before using.
